data.description: The pictures just do not do this home justice! Come tour this BEAUTIFUL newly built (2021) home right inside Columbia Lakes. This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is filled with all kinds of detailed upgrades like new kitchen backsplash, frosted pantry doors, and new light fixtures just to name a few. The formal dining room is just right off of the kitchen with plenty of space for those family Thanksgiving gatherings!   The kitchen is dressed in granite countertops, matching appliances, a breakfast table nook & a bar top that opens up to the living room. Who doesn't love a good open-concept home?   The primary bedroom has a convenient ensuite bathroom with his and hers sinks. Outside the back yard features a solid covered porch, the most needed when living in this Texas heat! It is also equipped with a new privacy fence, built June 2021, with a 2-year warranty!     Bring your family and come see this home for yourselves, your future awaits!
